週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1	Introduction & algorithm paradigm2	Introduction & algorithm paradigm3	Introduction & algorithm paradigm4	Partitioning 5	Partitioning 6	Floorplanning7	Floorplanning8	Placement9	Placement10	Global routing11	Global routing12	Detailed routing: full-chip routing and channel routing13	Detailed routing: full-chip routing and channel routing14	Specialized routing: clock routing, power/ground routing15	Post-layout optimization16	Design for manufacturability & reliability17          Emerging topics18          Emerging topics 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


